The evidence with the title 'Bill Owens (Colorado politician) - Wikipedia ' says William Forrester "Bill" Owens (born october 22, 1950) is an American politician, author and attorney who served as the 40th governor of Colorado from 1999 to 2007 . Owens was re-elected in 2002 by the largest majority in Colorado history, after making transportation , education, and tax cuts the focus of his governorship. 
